OL,6,FA Hampshire man who assaulted his
OL,7,Fformer business partner with a meat
OL,8,Fclaw has been jailed.
OL,10,FJonathan Oliver, aged 51, turned up
OL,11,Fthe victim's home address in the
OL,12,FPortchester area at around 7.55pm on
OL,13,F29 September 2022.
OL,15,FThe victim, in his 60s, was at home
OL,16,Fwith his wife when they were alerted
OL,17,Fto their rear patio doors being
OL,18,Fsmashed.
