OL,6,FThe victim sustained significant slash
OL,7,Fwounds and cuts, as well as 12
OL,8,Fpuncture wounds to his neck, and was
OL,9,Frushed to hospital for treatment.
OL,11,FOliver was subsequently arrested at
OL,12,Fhis home address in Catherington Lane,
OL,13,FWaterlooville, and charged with
OL,14,Fattempted murder.
OL,16,FThe case went to trial in Winchester
OL,17,Fin November 2023, where the jury found
OL,18,Fhim not guilty of attempted murder,
OL,19,Fand guilty of causing grievous bodily
OL,20,Fharm without intent.
