OL,6,FOn Monday, January 22, Oliver was
OL,7,Fjailed for 4 years, and handed an
OL,8,Findefinite Restraining Order.
OL,10,FPolice Staff Investigator Lynsey Jones
OL,11,Fsaid: "This was a terrifying ordeal
OL,12,Ffor the victim, and his wife, who was
OL,13,Ffaced with extreme violence in his own
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,F"There can be no excuse for what
OL,17,FJonathan Oliver did, and we want the
OL,18,Fpublic to be certain that we will
OL,19,Fnever tolerate any form of violence in
OL,20,Four community.
